title: Putin wants big turnout to legitimize election
text:
Putin wants big turnout to legitimize election   02:35 
Russian's go to the polls Sunday to pick their next President, with current leader Vladimir Putin all but certain to clinch another six years in the top job. But as Reuters Andrew Osborn explains, turnout will be key to his success.
